OPENCV HOUGH CIRCLES — REFERENCE
---------------------------------

Circle detection uses OpenCV's implementation of the Hough gradient method
for circles. For algorithm background, see OpenCV documentation and related
literature on the Hough transform. OpenCV itself is attributed under the
Apache License 2.0.


